{"questionId":"12218","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Let <strong><em>M</em></strong><sup>2</sup>&nbsp;= <strong><em>M</em></strong> where <strong><em>M</em></strong> =&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  a&amp;b \\\\   c&amp;d  \\end{array}} \\right){\\text{,}}\\,\\,bc \\ne 0\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>a</mi>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>b</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>c</mi>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>d</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>,</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>b</mi>\n  <mi>c</mi>\n  <mo>≠</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n</math></span>.&nbsp;</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p class=\"indent2\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;\">Find an expression for <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"bc\">\n  <mi>b</mi>\n  <mi>c</mi>\n</math></span> in terms of <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"a\">\n  <mi>a</mi>\n</math></span>.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{a^2} + bc = a\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>a</mi>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mi>b</mi>\n  <mi>c</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mi>a</mi>\n</math></span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>M1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" \\Rightarrow bc = a - {a^2}\">\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mi>b</mi>\n  <mi>c</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mi>a</